{"tid":944451,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[怨婦？]聖卡斯寸摩佬「嗰頭近」","createTime":"2018-12-17T07:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:29:52.000Z","uid":31626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32e3dea0ef695c10a38ee47e1984a4b2795ba381","tid":944451,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=KSPFNTxtngfSBhfgekmUh%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e1e9895c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯在周日英超雙紅會以1:3作客不敵利物浦，領隊摩連奴大受批評，曾於皇家馬德里跟他交惡的卡斯拿斯也忍不住抽抽水。<br />\n<br />\n卡斯拿斯（Iker Casillas）在twitter中表示：「根據葡萄牙報章，某人說我這個年齡（37歲）的球員，處於生涯的尾聲，我完全同意！不過我的疑問是，以領隊來說，何時或去到哪個階段，你們才會看到他不再執教？」<br />\n<br />\n雖然聖卡斯的tweet沒有指名道姓，但在雙紅會之後發出，明眼人都知道他是暗寸摩連奴。事關2人積怨甚深，當摩佬於2010至13年執教皇家馬德里，跟卡斯拿斯交惡，更把他貶為後備，間接導致這名青訓出身的隊長於2015年離隊。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯於周日英超雙紅會，雖然有攻中連格一度追平，但被翼鋒梳頓沙基利於尾段連轟2球，以1:3作客不敵利物浦。紅魔賽後跟榜首紅軍相差19分，跟前4亦有11分距離。"},{"pid":"a4fbba567f50003a8c5734f1e01106f5ccb2f648","tid":944451,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8032ae208b4797eb3887f83f53429c42ffc55a95","tid":944451,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"聖卡離隊個時，好似摩佬先串： 可以去拎人生未拎過獎(歐霸). <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a385b7000a4108fcfef4c682370049874562908","tid":944451,"uid":141519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"on9拉摩斯"},{"pid":"6766e7fdf7e95d7a3417763ea913e8b33e8d8ff3","tid":944451,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:54:50.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5752fec0ad97cb87e2f5f50f0dedf9f2ffa47922","tid":944451,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"算有口德啦 你睇下曼聯果班名宿屌得仲狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ca4cfd1bdf929a3c624239d25d4f5e661d8f0e","tid":944451,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"最衰拉莫斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}